Welcome to RiftsMUD.

This is a text-based roleplaying game set on Rifts Earth, a post-apocalyptic
world shattered by dimensional rifts.  You are a survivor in a dangerous and
richly detailed world.

BASIC MOVEMENT
  Type a direction to move: north, south, east, west (or n, s, e, w).
  Some rooms have up, down, and other directions as well.

LOOKING AROUND
  look                  describes your current room
  look <object>         examines something in the room
  look at <object>      same as above

YOUR CHARACTER
  score                 displays your stats, level, and condition
  inventory (or inv)    lists what you are carrying
  worn                  shows what you are wearing or wielding

COMMUNICATION
  say <text>            speak aloud to people in the same room
  ooc <text>            out-of-character global chat channel
  tell <name> <text>    private message to another player
  who                   lists players currently online
  introduce             introduces yourself to nearby players

HELP SYSTEM
  help                  opens the help menu
  help <topic>          looks up a specific topic
  Useful topics: combat, skills, improve, advance, score, races, occs, weapons, colour

QUESTS
  quests                lists your active and completed quests
  Talk to NPCs and explore to find quest givers.

CONTACT STAFF
  If you have a question, type: ooc <your question here>
  Wizards (staff) can see the OOC channel and will help when available.

See also: combat, stats, races, occs, skills, quests, score
